<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title><%= @name %></title>
<style>
body {
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  background-color: #F8F8F8;;
  color: #000;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

.container {
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 40px auto;
  padding: 60px;
  background-color: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 10px;
}

h1 {
  color: #2A86FF;
  margin-bottom: 0px;
  margin-top: 0px;
  font-size: 25px;
  max-width: 100%;
  word-break: break-word; /* breaks long words */
  overflow-wrap: break-word; /* for broader browser support */
  white-space: normal; /* allow normal wrapping */
  display: -webkit-box;
  -webkit-line-clamp: 20; /* max 2 lines */
  -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
  overflow: hidden;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
}

h2 {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  margin-top: 0px;
  font-size: 20px;
}

p {
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.4;
  color: rgba(19, 36, 65, 0.56);
}

ul {
  padding-left: 20px;
}

a {
   color: #2A86FF;
  text-decoration: none;
}

li {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.logo {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .container {
    margin: 30px;
    padding: 40px;
  }
  p {
    font-size: 15px;
  }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
 <div class = "logo">
    <a href="https://grovs.io"><%= image_tag "logo-large-black.svg", alt: "grovs - logo" %></a>
  </div>
  <br>
  <h1><%= @name %></h1>
<br>
<p>This is your default redirect page.</p>
<p>You are accessing this URL on a platform where redirects are not currently enabled. If you are the app developer, you can enable specific redirects (such as websites or App Stores) for this platform through the dashboard.</p>
<br>
  <p>To update these settings, navigate to your project’s redirect configuration under <a href="https://app.grovs.io">Configuration -> Redirect</a>.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>